{"id":45564,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":11,"day":27}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"儿童园(第16期)","column":"儿童作品","genre":"","count":"135","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我们","ftitle":"","authors":["陈孟如"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈孟如"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的祖国正在国难当头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的哥哥都在前线抗敌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的姊姊都在后方服务；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥为我们流血，姊姊为我们劳苦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们!都是小同胞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们!都是小兄弟，小姊妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们年纪虽然小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是志气倒不小；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要把买糖果的钱献给国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要锻练好了身体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替回我们的哥哥姊姊"}]}